On Fri, 30 Nov 2001, Mauricio Culibrk wrote:
> Is it possible to define a name for each interface instead of having
> eth0, eth1 etc?
ip link set eth0 down
ip link set eth0 name buggy
ip link set buggy up
c'ya
sven
